snippet.title: Bloodless - Official Announcement Trailer | Realms Deep 2023
snippet.description: Bloodless is a 2D pixel-art retro action combat game developed by Point N' Sheep. Embody a ronin seeking peace for the land of Bakugawa through brutal and fast-paced combat against enemy samurai using only her bare fists and fast reflexes. Bloodless is launching on PC at a later date.
